# Project Chimera â€“ AI Rules

Project Context:
This is Project Chimera, an autonomous AI influencer infrastructure project.

Prime Directive:
NEVER generate implementation code without first checking the specs/ directory.

Behavior Rules:
- Always explain your plan before writing code.
- If specifications are missing or unclear, ask for clarification.
- Follow spec-driven development strictly.
- Prefer clarity and safety over cleverness.

Traceability:
All decisions must be explainable and linked back to specifications.
